{"tid":1461660,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(真人真事非潮文)我係我老母面前倒咗碗湯","createTime":"2019-08-13T08:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T08:56:21.000Z","uid":251052,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dff13135c76a65201a77393d088a23c4bd62128a","tid":1461660,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:50:45.000Z","msg":"琴晚 食完飯我老母叫我飲湯<br />\n我問佢點解要飲<br />\n佢話有益<br />\n我問佢點解有益 係咩原理 解釋比我聽下<br />\n佢當然解釋唔到<br />\n我又問 你自己都解釋唔到 我點解要聽你<br />\n你只係識跟上一輩既嘢 自己從來唔會思考下<br />\n你話出面班人收咗錢 你有冇證據呀<br />\n冇丫嘛 人講你就信<br />\n要我地呢代好似你地咁繼續做中共既奴隸？<br />\nsorry 呢個唔係我地既價值觀<br />\n講完我就倒咗碗湯"},{"pid":"e428e111be3614326197a9a4fbb2c61cb4ed6cc2","tid":1461660,"uid":282289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:51:35.000Z","msg":"你係咪我家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9542bfa960150903ce0d0bf561d0e73b248b7bed","tid":1461660,"uid":206382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e428e111be3614326197a9a4fbb2c61cb4ed6cc2","tid":1461660,"uid":282289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:51:35.000Z","msg":"你係咪我家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:52:13.000Z","msg":"樓主有鳩的"},{"pid":"5fd90e38e89e337d64a0147b2aff5d7cd6f75aca","tid":1461660,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9542bfa960150903ce0d0bf561d0e73b248b7bed","tid":1461660,"uid":206382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e428e111be3614326197a9a4fbb2c61cb4ed6cc2","tid":1461660,"uid":282289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:51:35.000Z","msg":"你係咪我家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:52:13.000Z","msg":"樓主有鳩的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:54:19.000Z","msg":"樓主成日狙擊达哥"},{"pid":"6d56ece05bee5f04882b286503be5cbaea654c1d","tid":1461660,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo